headline: CVS Health declares quarterly dividend
summary: CVS Health® (NYSE: CVS) has announced that its board of directors has approved a quarterly dividend of sixty-six and one-half cents ($0.665 cents) per share on the Common Stock of the Corporation. The dividend is payable on August 1, 2025, to holders of record on July 22, 2025.
